Interface SerializableRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasHeaders, RequestOptions
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ProcessableRequest, SerializableRequestInProcess

    public interface SerializableRequest
extends RequestOptions, HasHeaders

    A request capable of being serialized.

    Serialization should happen only once.
